                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Yeah, but the map hasn't changed in years... Since that's what we are interested in, the original site is fine.
<br />

<br />
Also I should warn you that when you go through the painting in the main hall, if you are levitating (and you should always be levitating in PoM) and you are too far off the ground you will get stuck in a empty space inside the wall and there is no way to get out. So make sure you push against the floor when going through that painting.
<br />

<br />
This raid made me miss the real PoM again but I just have to accept that the devs killed the zone and there's nothing to do about it.
<br />

<br />
I miss you, Sniffles!
