                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Regarding the ASE fight in PoM:
<br />

<br />
The suggestion for 4 groups is right on.   With 3 groups of mostly Time/Qvic enabled (some hydras) we wiped.
<br />

<br />
With 3.5 groups we <span style="text-decoration: underline">barely</span> won on the second try after adding a couple extra clerics and a wizzy.  We were mostly OOM at the end.  MGB heals helped a lot and if you can get pallies to help with group heals it will definitely help.  Also, if you can get a bst or two that can mass paragon that would help a bunch with the mana drain component of the dot.  
<br />

<br />
This guy has a crapload of HPs so take as much dps as you can.  No problem with adds, just pull the misc trash near the corner marked in the map above.  
<br />

<br />
Try for overkill if it's an option  <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=398958" target="_blank" class="postlink">Aliie (Lazy-Eye) Baba</a>
